Aliens of the Deep;;49;;84;;G;;Director James Cameron travels with the crew of a Russian research vessel as they plunge into the depths of the ocean to explore hypothermal vents. These fissures in the Earth's surface are known to be the home of strange and unusual sea creatures, unlike anything found anywhere else on Earth. While exploring these rarely seen environments, scientists discuss the similarities between these ecosystems and the environments that may be found on alien planets.;;Documentary;;James Cameron,Steven Quale;;2005;;James Cameron,Pamela Conrad,Djanna Figueroa,Kevin Peter Hand,Loretta Hidalgo,Maya Tolstoy;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/aliens_of_the_deep